  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b87\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The body of the missing student who got stuck in the sea and was dragged away was recovered",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The body of a school student who went missing after getting caught in the sea in Periya Neelawani Police Division of Amparai District has been recovered.",
        "3 students were swept away by the sea waves when they went to bathe in the Theertha Utsavam on the final day of the Periyathambiran Temple Utsavam.",
        "In this case, two students managed to reach the shore while another student was dragged into the sea and disappeared.",
        "The body of a 16-year-old respected student named Rasanayakam Sanujan from Periyaneelavani 1 area, who had gone missing, was recovered from the shore on Wednesday (27) evening and taken to Kalmunai Asrap Memorial Hospital for post-mortem examination.",
        "Around 16-year-old school students were thus trapped in this situation and despite the fact that the sea was unusually turbulent, they were engaged in swimming in the sea.",
        "While going to the coastal area as usual, it was dragged into the sea. Two of them were rescued and the other student was rescued by the navy, seafarers and their relatives.",
        "Further, the dead body will be handed over to the relatives after post-mortem examination and Periya Neelawani police are conducting investigations regarding the incident."
      ],
